title: Dorlands Spellcheck.iso
description:
======================================================================
		Dorland&#039;s Electronic Medical Speller
			   Version 4.0   
======================================================================

Dorland&#039;s Electronic Medical Speller.  This
new version of our medical speller recognizes more than 275,000 medical
terms, and is compatible with the latest versions of the most popular
word processing programs.


About Dorland&#039;s Electronic Medical Speller:
===========================================

Dorland&#039;s Electronic Medical Speller recognizes more than 275,000 terms
from the medical field.  Terms included cover all medical specialties
compiled from the most reliable sources in the medical field. 

===========================================

Software included with this iso:

Dorland&#039;s Medical SpellChecker for various word processing apps.  This spellchecker is compatible with the following software:

     
     MS Word               
              7.0
              8.0
              9.0
             10.0
             11.0

     MS Office
               95
               97
             2000
               XP
             2003
         NOT 2007

     Corel/Wordperfect
              7.0
              8.0
              9.0
             10.0
             11.0
 
     Lotus
              WordPro 97
              WordPro Millenium (9.x)

As far as I have been able to tell, this version is NOT COMPATIBLE WITH MS Office/Word 2007, so don&#039;t waste your and my time by asking.

Also included are dictionary installations for PalmOS handhelds and Windows Mobile equipped devices (PocketPC).  These bonuses came packaged with MobiPocket reader with seems to require registration at their site.  I personally don&#039;t need the mobile readers so your on your own regarding how to activate and use them.

This upload is in tribute to MEDISO, a group that goes out of their way to bring valuable medical-genre content to a select group of downloaders.  Thanks guys!  Searth TPB for MEDISO and you&#039;ll find them.

ISO was created using Alcohol 120% and is completely virus free.

ENJOY!
